 an "M2" monk, by definition some of these are guesswork; I've tried to indicate this with a "?". Somewhat arbitrarily, I've ordered them by knowledge/difficulty level.</p><br><table border="1" width="100%" height="576"> <tr><td width="25%" height="19"><b>Zone:</b></td><td width="75%" height="19"><b>Area/Monk Range</b>:</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Cazic Thule</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">lizards-M3(?), oozes/fish/mosquitoes M2</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Ssra</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">Can't see a monk handling elites easily.      M3(????)</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Seru</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">Ditto on Lictors etc. M3(?????)</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Deep Chardok</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2 to kennels, library(?).</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Deep DN</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2*</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Siren's Grotto</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2*</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">PoG</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">PoF/PoH</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M1</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Howling Stones</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M1</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Sebelis-Juggs/Reets</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Deeper KD</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2 (Arena, Bank, etc)</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19"></td>    <td width="75%" height="19"></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19"><b>Less familiar:</b></td>    <td width="75%" height="19"></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Maiden's Eye</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M1-Goranga. Not sure of rest, don't exp them.</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">IWK</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Acrylia</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Akheva</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M2?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Umbral Planes</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M3?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Deeper Hole</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M1?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">Griegs</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">?</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="19">The Deep</td>    <td width="75%" height="19">M3? M1-2 at edges.</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="25%" height="20"></td>    <td width="75%" height="20"></td>  </tr></table><br>* Haven't hunted here extensively since caster rebuffing, so these are<br>somewhat guesswork atm.<br><p>I haven't bothered including places that are generally sub 1 group -- Fungus Grove, Velketors, Karnors Castle, The Grey, etc. Similarly, places that are not great exp/loot at 60 are left out. I probably should have left HS out, but I kind of like it.<br><br>I appreciate community feedback on everything.</p><br>Sister Katriona Swiftsilver, Five Rings, Luclin.<br> <p><center>Norrath's only <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=124106">Celtic monk</a>. <a href="http://www.five-rings.com">Five Rings</a>.</center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucatrinofluclin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Catrin of Luclin</A> at: 7/17/02 10:20:13 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uchenkovcalgar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Chenkov Calgar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=us